snippet.title: Tamarak Trail - Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to PC & consoles in 2023 - Wishlist Now on Steam: https://rebrand.ly/TamarakTrailAnnounce

Tamarak Trail is a deck-building roguelike. Instead of cards, you'll use a customizable dice set to battle through randomly generated trails - full of loot, mysteries, and danger to protect inhabitants from the evil that has corrupted the trail.

NEVER MISS OUT ON NEWS!
SUBSCRIBE: https://bit.ly/2IPMij9
FOLLOW US: https://allmylinks.com/tamarak-trail
